{"tid":990377,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港女被遣返】遊台到咖啡店當一日女僕 涉做黑工被捕","createTime":"2019-01-21T13:55:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T13:22:04.000Z","uid":29627,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"97ba79ff4c2051a5eeb8ab2ebbf2519461340d01","tid":990377,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:55:49.000Z","msg":"【港女被遣返】遊台到咖啡店當一日女僕 涉做黑工被捕 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190121/large/1548074294_c557.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190121%2Flarge%2F1548074294_c557.jpg&h=a2647df3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n來自香港的譚姓女子到台灣代言女僕活動，被指違法遭遣返。<br />\n<br />\n台灣桃園近來興起日本女僕咖啡店，移民署桃園市專勤隊接獲民眾檢舉，指一名來自香港的譚姓女子以觀光名義遊台，卻以女僕裝扮從事代言活動，擔任一日女僕工作。專勤隊員暗中搜集證據，確認事實後，依規定重罰僱主，並將譚女強制遣送出境。<br />\n<br />\n根據台灣移民署調查，這名綽號玲玲的譚姓女子，長相甜美，五官端正，多次以觀光名義遊台。這次入境不久後，譚女即前往高雄一間咖啡廳，從事女僕交流活動。至昨日，譚女到桃園中壢區一間咖啡店代言，她穿起女僕裝，上台即興表演，招攬生意，希望顧客給她支持與鼓勵。移民署人員暗中搜集證據，隨後表露身份，將譚女帶返移民署問話。<br />\n<br />\n譚女供稱，她透過facebook認識台灣女僕同好，到當地後想與當地喜歡女僕文化的人士交流，並不清楚這樣會違反台灣的法例規定。<br />\n<br />\n台灣移民署再次呼籲當地僱主，如未經申請許可，僱用或介紹港、澳居民在台灣工作，恐違反《香港澳門關係條例》、《香港澳門居民進入台灣地區及居留定居許可辦法》等相關規定。譚女從事與旅遊觀光不符的活動或工作，可被強制出境並管制入境，僱主及中間人除最高可被罰款75萬元（新台幣；約19萬港元）外，5年內再犯者還會觸犯刑責，可被判監。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190121/59168901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190121%2F59168901&d=1L79tNmClEUrvu3H0gBFjMP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=888963d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190121%2F59168901&h=d92e5d1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190121/59168901</a><br />\n<br />\n長相甜美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d93f012df33602d9dd42485cb92381dd299cd0c","tid":990377,"uid":165482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ef738c2c171c2761b8b5f42898412a93418104","tid":990377,"uid":81518,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:01:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06ba4d956bf192d571a9fe6e4f92cf6e2736a0c9","tid":990377,"uid":155818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:03:42.000Z","msg":"鼻哥窿有點大"},{"pid":"24417d5f91770728b5f19b283e3cc90ce91dc88b","tid":990377,"uid":3241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:05:53.000Z","msg":"上次香港拉左個日本妹好似告埋上法庭， 台灣佬做野真係輕手"},{"pid":"58e9941d22df310347e13887ede1944be8126528","tid":990377,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:46:22.000Z","msg":"長相甜美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b4ace2d5dcaef5c16f942614228f0c80444c21","tid":990377,"uid":6752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"58e9941d22df310347e13887ede1944be8126528","tid":990377,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:46:22.000Z","msg":"長相甜美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:48:12.000Z","msg":"記者盡左力"},{"pid":"d9641ec8cec6fa443238238427b8d686f8d6dcda","tid":990377,"uid":81518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:50:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"90e9c49cb594d4733921e50866afc7a0981acc5c","tid":990377,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:51:12.000Z","msg":"個鼻好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1db854d2da3f0ef2e90b94056